001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 13,
011    displayName = "Time Change",
012    internalName = "LID_TIME_CHANGED",
013    usedByTidepool = true
014)
015public class TimeChangedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
016    
017    private long timePrior;
018    private long timeAfter;
019    private long rawRTC;
020    
021    public TimeChangedHistoryLog() {}
022    public TimeChangedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
023        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
024        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, timePrior, timeAfter, rawRTC);
025        this.timePrior = timePrior;
026        this.timeAfter = timeAfter;
027        this.rawRTC = rawRTC;
028        
029    }
030
031    public TimeChangedHistoryLog(long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
032        this(0, 0, timePrior, timeAfter, rawRTC);
033    }
034
035    public int typeId() {
036        return 13;
037    }
038
039    /**
040     * <table border="1">
041     * <caption>Parsed fields for TimeChangedHistoryLog:</caption>
042     * <tr><td><code>timePrior</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>timeAfter</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>rawRTC</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
045     * </table>
046     */
047    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
048        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
049        this.cargo = raw;
050        parseBase(raw);
051        this.timePrior = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10);
052        this.timeAfter = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14);
053        this.rawRTC = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
054        
055    }
056
057    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long timePrior, long timeAfter, long rawRTC) {
058        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
059            new byte[]{13, 0},
060            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
061            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
062            Bytes.toUint32(timePrior), 
063            Bytes.toUint32(timeAfter), 
064            Bytes.toUint32(rawRTC)));
065    }
066    public long getTimePrior() {
067        return timePrior;
068    }
069    public long getTimeAfter() {
070        return timeAfter;
071    }
072    public long getRawRTC() {
073        return rawRTC;
074    }
075    
076}
